data.value:
Developped by José Ángel (@torbol)
1. Connect your phone and be sure to have activated USB debugging in your device system settings, under Developer options.
2. Push Start Daemon and connect to stablish a connection with your phone, accept all warnings in your phone
3. Once detected (phone detected will be checked), you can proceed to push the Backup button. Wait until it ends.
